A thin converging lens has a focal length of 20 cm. An object is placed 30 cm from the lens. Calculate the image distance from the lens. What type of image is formed? 

	ext{(A)} 60 	ext{ cm, virtual} 
	ext{(B)} 60 	ext{ cm, real} 
	ext{(C)} 12 	ext{ cm, real} 
	ext{(D)} -12 	ext{ cm, virtual}
